 prolly be rude.";s:9:"timestamp";s:10:"1429927293";s:15:"chat_name_color";s:7:"#ffa100";s:9:"chat_rand";s:11:"14299272897";s:15:"chat_text_color";s:7:"#ff7400";s:16:"chat_log_type_id";s:1:"1";s:6:"viewed";N;}i:1331662;a:14:{s:11:"chat_log_id";s:7:"1331662";s:12:"chat_room_id";s:1:"4";s:7:"user_id";s:5:"12019";s:6:"handle";s:4:"Ezki";s:12:"character_id";s:4:"1337";s:17:"recipient_user_id";N;s:18:"recipient_username";N;s:4:"text";s:276:"/me flicks her ears and looks up, glancing around quickly before she notices StarOcean. She squints some, trying to recognize the orange blur in the distance. She book marks her reading material and shuts it for now, getting up and moving over to StarOcean. &quot;Hello?&quot;";s:9:"timestamp";s:10:"1429927675";s:15:"chat_name_color";s:7:"#9999ff";s:9:"chat_rand";s:11:"14299276647";s:15:"chat_text_color";s:7:"#ffffff";s:16:"chat_log_type_id";s:1:"1";s:6:"viewed";N;}i:1331663;a:14:{s:11:"chat_log_id";s:7:"1331663";s:12:"chat_room_id";s:1:"4";s:7:"user_id";s:2:"38";s:6:"handle";s:9:"StarOcean";s:12:"character_id";s:3:"223";s:17:"recipient_user_id";N;s:18:"recipient_username";N;s:4:"text";s:235:"/me bounds the rest of the way and skids a lil, smiling big and waving happily! &quot;Hey there! You&#039;re the one from town square, right? Who i took out for the snack?&quot; It was kind of hard to forget, but she wanted to be sure!";s:9:"timestamp";s:10:"1429927831";s:15:"chat_name_color";s:7:"#ffa100";s:9:"chat_rand";s:11:"14299278286";s:15:"chat_text_color";s:7:"#ff7400";s:16:"chat_log_type_id";s:1:"1";s:6:"viewed";N;}i:1331667;a:14:{s:11:"chat_log_id";s:7:"1331667";s:12:"chat_room_id";s:1:"4";s:7:"user_id";s:5:"12019";s:6:"handle";s:4:"Ezki";s:12:"character_id";s:4:"1337";s:17:"recipient_user_id";N;s:18:"recipient_username";N;s:4:"text";s:283:"/me smiles once StarOcean was close enough and says &quot;Oh, Miss Ocean. Y-yes, that is correct. I am grateful for the meal you gifted me.&quot; The filly does a bow and says &quot;Vhat is... pardon, vhat are these items you carry?&quot; She eyes the swimming gear somewhat confused";s:9:"timestamp";s:10:"1429928154";s:15:"chat_name_color";s:7:"#9999ff";s:9:"chat_rand";s:11:"14299281440";s:15:"chat_text_color";s:7:"#ffffff";s:16:"chat_log_type_id";s:1:"1";s:6:"viewed";N;}i:1331670;a:14:{s:11:"chat_log_id";s:7:"1331670";s:12:"chat_room_id";s:1:"4";s:7:"user_id";s:2:"38";s:6:"handle";s:9:"StarOcean";s:12:"character_id";s:3:"223";s:17:"recipient_user_id";N;s:18:"recipient_username";N;s:4:"text";s:550:"&quot;Huh- Oh! Hehe, i&#039;m going swimming!&quot; She chirps, giggling and nearly hopping in place. She -loved- to swim! &quot;Here, looky!&quot; She plops down and pulls out an odd looking snorkel, copper and blue with runes carved up the tube, and little searchlights next to the goggles. &quot;You can store air in the tube and then have like a mini scuba breather so you can stay down longer!&quot; She explains happily, for once keeping her explanation simple instead of rambling about the specific runic functions or some other such nonsense.";s:9:"timestamp";s:10:"1429928435";s:15:"chat_name_color";s:7:"#ffa100";s:9:"chat_rand";s:11:"14299284322";s:15:"chat_text_color";s:7:"#ff7400";s:16:"chat_log_type_id";s:1:"1";s:6:"viewed";N;}i:1331671;a:14:{s:11:"chat_log_id";s:7:"1331671";s:12:"chat_room_id";s:1:"4";s:7:"user_id";s:5:"12019";s:6:"handle";s:4:"Ezki";s:12:"character_id";s:4:"1337";s:17:"recipient_user_id";N;s:18:"recipient_username";N;s:4:"text";s:272:"&quot;Svimming?&quot; she asks blinking. &quot;Surely you-&quot; she starts before thinking about it. &quot;Oh. That vould actually vork here, vouldn&#039;t it.&quot; she says entirely to herself before looking back to StarOcean. &quot;Pardon but vhat is mini scuba?&quot;";s:9:"timestamp";s:10:"1429928871";s:15:"chat_name_color";s:7:"#9999ff";s:9:"chat_rand";s:11:"14299288603";s:15:"chat_text_color";s:7:"#ffffff";s:16:"chat_log_type_id";s:1:"1";s:6:"viewed";N;}i:1331672;a:14:{s:11:"chat_log_id";s:7:"1331672";s:12:"chat_room_id";s:1:"4";s:7:"user_id";s:2:"38";s:6:"handle";s:9:"StarOcean";s:12:"character_id";s:3:"223";s:17:"recipient_user_id";N;s:18:"recipient_username";N;s:4:"text";s:207:"/me blinks slowly, tilting her head some. &quot;You.. Don&#039;t know what a scuba is?&quot; She asks a bit hesitantly, not remembering that this was a pony from up north where -nopony- prolly swam outdoors.";s:9:"timestamp";s:10:"1429928927";s:15:"chat_name_color";s:7:"#ffa100";s:9:"chat_rand";s:11:"14299289239";s:15:"chat_text_color";s:7:"#ff7400";s:16:"chat_log_type_id";s:1:"1";s:6:"viewed";N;}i:1331673;a:14:{s:11:"chat_log_id";s:7:"1331673";s:12:"chat_room_id";s:1:"4";s:7:"user_id";s:5:"12019";s:6:"handle";s:4:"Ezki";s:12:"character_id";s:4:"1337";s:17:"recipient_user_id";N;s:18:"recipient_username";N;s:4:"text";s:370:"&quot;I am afradi not. Vhere I come from, svimming usually means freezing to death.&quot; she says a bit sadly. &quot;I never learnt how to svim, although I know some of the clans in the south have saunas and for some reason enjoy varming themselves before leaping into freezing vater. My father says such behaviour is foolish, but I have not vitnessed it myself..&quot;";s:9:"timestamp";s:10:"1429929187";s:15:"chat_name_color";s:7:"#9999ff";s:9:"chat_rand";s:11:"14299291768";s:15:"chat_text_color";s:7:"#ffffff";s:16:"chat_log_type_id";s:1:"1";s:6:"viewed";N;}i:1331674;a:14:{s:11:"chat_log_id";s:7:"1331674";s:12:"chat_room_id";s:1:"4";s:7:"user_id";s:2:"38";s:6:"handle";s:9:"StarOcean";s:12:"character_id";s:3:"223";s:17:"recipient_user_id";N;s:18:"recipient_username";N;s:4:"text";s:429:"/me giggles lots at the mental image, grinning some! &quot;Hehe, that kinda sounds hilarious.. Idunno if i&#039;d try it though, i like swimming in warmer water more. Gotta use a sub for the cold and deep stuff.&quot; She nodnods seriously. &quot;You wanna learn?&quot; She asks out of nowhere suddenly. &quot;I&#039;ve taught some ponies before, it&#039;s not hard at all!&quot; Swimming was -very- serious business, yes it was!";s:9:"timestamp";s:10:"1429929545";s:15:"chat_name_color";s:7:"#ffa100";s:9:"chat_rand";s:11:"14299295424";s:15:"chat_text_color";s:7:"#ff7400";s:16:"chat_log_type_id";s:1:"1";s:6:"viewed";N;}i:1331675;a:14:{s:11:"chat_log_id";s:7:"1331675";s:12:"chat_room_id";s:1:"4";s:7:"user_id";s:5:"12019";s:6:"handle";s:4:"Ezki";s:12:"character_id";s:4:"1337";s:17:"recipient_user_id";N;s:18:"recipient_username";N;s:4:"text";s:141:"&quot;V-vhat? Learn to svim? I can barely say the vord let alone do it!&quot; she says, shaking her head quickly &quot;Vhat if I drown?&quot;";s:9:"timestamp";s:10:"1429929614";s:15:"chat_name_color";s:7:"#9999ff";s:9:"chat_rand";s:11:"14299296040";s:15:"chat_text_color";s:7:"#ffffff";s:16:"chat_log_type_id";s:1:"1";s:6:"viewed";N;}i:1331677;a:14:{s:11:"chat_log_id";s:7:"1331677";s:12:"chat_room_id";s:1:"4";s:7:"user_id";s:2:"38";s:6:"handle";s:9:"StarOcean";s:12:"character_id";s:3:"223";s:17:"recipient_user_id";N;s:18:"recipient_username";N;s:4:"text";s:560:"&quot;I would never let you,&quot; she replies seriously, nodding. Swimming was serious. Business. Everypony needed to know how! Geez, she should have been a lifeguard or something.. &quot;That&#039;s the attitude that you have to get over. Your body already knows how, swimming is what you instinctively do so you don&#039;t die. Your brain just wants to panic is all.&quot; Noooooot the best pep talk perhaps, but it was technically true, probably. She wasn&#039;t gonna take and throw the poor pony in the lake or anything though, she was too nice for that.";s:9:"timestamp";s:10:"1429930000";s:15:"chat_name_color";s:7:"#ffa100";s:9:"chat_rand";s:11:"14299299966";s:15:"chat_text_color";s:7:"#ff7400";s:16:"chat_log_type_id";s:1:"1";s:6:"viewed";N;}i:1331678;a:14:{s:11:"chat_log_id";s:7:"1331678";s:12:"chat_room_id";s:1:"4";s:7:"user_id";s:5:"12019";s:6:"handle";s:4:"Ezki";s:12:"character_id";s:4:"1337";s:17:"recipient_user_id";N;s:18:"recipient_username";N;s:4:"text";s:232:"/me sits down and breaths quickly &quot;I do not think I am ready for this Miss Ocean. I have not even read anything about svimming techniques or, vhat to do in the case of drowning, or or or or-&quot; Ezki hyperventilates a little.";s:9:"timestamp";s:10:"1429930222";s:15:"chat_name_color";s:7:"#9999ff";s:9:"chat_rand";s:11:"14299302120";s:15:"chat_text_color";s:7:"#ffffff";s:16:"chat_log_type_id";s:1:"1";s:6:"viewed";N;}i:1331679;a:14:{s:11:"chat_log_id";s:7:"1331679";s:12:"chat_room_id";s:1:"4";s:7:"user_id";s:2:"38";s:6:"handle";s:9:"StarOcean";s:12:"character_id";s:3:"223";s:17:"recipient_user_id";N;s:18:"recipient_username";N;s:4:"text";s:314:"&quot;Relax, relax..!&quot; Stary&#039;s eyes widen a little and she looks around nervously, before trying to calm her down. &quot;It&#039;s okay, we don&#039;t have to! We can.. Ummm, find a big dry green field and just hang out there! No water at all! Not even any to drink, i&#039;ll leave my cooler here!&quot;";s:9:"timestamp";s:10:"1429930480";s:15:"chat_name_color";s:7:"#ffa100";s:9:"chat_rand";s:11:"14299304772";s:15:"chat_text_color";s:7:"#ff7400";s:16:"chat_log_type_id";s:1:"1";s:6:"viewed";N;}i:1331681;a:14:{s:11:"chat_log_id";s:7:"1331681";s:12:"chat_room_id";s:1:"4";s:7:"user_id";s:5:"12019";s:6:"handle";s:4:"Ezki";s:12:"character_id";s:4:"1337";s:17:"recipient_user_id";N;s:18:"recipient_username";N;s:4:"text";s:379:"/me breathes a little more slowly as she starts to calm down, nodding a bit. &quot;Yes, you are correct. I should relax. My apologies.&quot; she says, panting a bit and then exhaling deeply. &quot;I am deeply sorry, I just am not ready for that. I will read up on it and then, I think I vill be. If it is not too much to ask, could you... teach me then?&quot; she asks hopefully.";s:9:"timestamp";s:10:"1429930743";s:15:"chat_name_color";s:7:"#9999ff";s:9:"chat_rand";s:11:"14299307323";s:15:"chat_text_color";s:7:"#ffffff";s:16:"chat_log_type_id";s:1:"1";s:6:"viewed";N;}i:1331682;a:14:{s:11:"chat_log_id";s:7:"1331682";s:12:"chat_room_id";s:1:"4";s:7:"user_id";s:2:"38";s:6:"handle";s:9:"StarOcean";s:12:"character_id";s:3:"223";s:17:"recipient_user_id";N;s:18:"recipient_username";N;s:4:"text";s:666:"/me immediately perks up herself! &quot;Totally! Hehe, swimming&#039;s the -best-, you&#039;ll love it! If you want a better place i -know- i could bum my bestie&#039;s pool for it, she wouldn&#039;t mind at all!&quot; Pools were a much safer and more controlled environment for learning to swim, besides. &quot;If you wore the snorkel you wouldn&#039;t run out of air, but that&#039;s besides the point. I could letcha borrow a book or two, but well.. They&#039;re more -about- the ocean, they don&#039;t really -teach-.. Heh.. Actually the one about the giant killer squid and the alien base on the seafloor might be a little much..&quot; She trails off awkwardly.";s:9:"timestamp";s:10:"1429931052";s:15:"chat_name_color";s:7:"#ffa100";s:9:"chat_rand";s:11:"14299310495";s:15:"chat_text_color";s:7:"#ff7400";s:16:"chat_log_type_id";s:1:"1";s:6:"viewed";N;}i:1331684;a:14:{s:11:"chat_log_id";s:7:"1331684";s:12:"chat_room_id";s:1:"4";s:7:"user_id";s:5:"12019";s:6:"handle";s:4:"Ezki";s:12:"character_id";s:4:"1337";s:17:"recipient_user_id";N;s:18:"recipient_username";N;s:4:"text";s:301:"/me pauses and seems confused again &quot;P-pardon? Bum your.. besti&#039;es pool?&quot; she says slowly as if it would make more sense that way. She then freezes up (which is easy for Ezki) and says &quot;I vould very much like to borrow your books but I am not sure about giant killer sqvuids.&quot;";s:9:"timestamp";s:10:"1429931580";s:15:"chat_name_color";s:7:"#9999ff";s:9:"chat_rand";s:11:"14299315693";s:15:"chat_text_color";s:7:"#ffffff";s:16:"chat_log_type_id";s:1:"1";s:6:"viewed";N;}i:1331687;a:14:{s:11:"chat_log_id";s:7:"1331687";s:12:"chat_room_id";s:1:"4";s:7:"user_id";s:2:"38";s:6:"handle";s:9:"StarOcean";s:12:"character_id";s:3:"223";s:17:"recipient_user_id";N;s:18:"recipient_username";N;s:4:"text";s:602:"&quot;Weeeeeeell.. They&#039;re kinda like.. Adventure stories.. Scifi mags.. There are a few educational ones too though, but they&#039;re not really about swimming so much as about ocean stuff,&quot; she explains brightly. &quot;I have like, -boxes- of back issues of Equestrian Geographic too! There&#039;s a decent number of articles in those, buuuuuut.. Prolly won&#039;t help you when it comes to learning to swim. Might wanna check the library. I still don&#039;t think swimming&#039;s something you&#039;re supposed to learn out of a book though..&quot; She pouts softly, cheeks all puffed out.";s:9:"timestamp";s:10:"1429931748";s:15:"chat_name_color";s:7:"#ffa100";s:9:"chat_rand";s:11:"14299317454";s:15:"chat_text_color";s:7:"#ff7400";s:16:"chat_log_type_id";s:1:"1";s:6:"viewed";N;}i:1331688;a:14:{s:11:"chat_log_id";s:7:"1331688";s:12:"chat_room_id";s:1:"4";s:7:"user_id";s:5:"12019";s:6:"handle";s:4:"Ezki";s:12:"character_id";s:4:"1337";s:17:"recipient_user_id";N;s:18:"recipient_username";N;s:4:"text";s:183:"&quot;Everyday I am reminded I have much to learn.&quot; she says meekly but with a smile. &quot;I vill check the library but I am still interested in the material you speak of.&quot;";s:9:"timestamp";s:10:"1429931810";s:15:"chat_name_color";s:7:"#9999ff";s:9:"chat_rand";s:11:"14299317996";s:15:"chat_text_color";s:7:"#ffffff";s:16:"chat_log_type_id";s:1:"1";s:6:"viewed";N;}i:1331690;a:14:{s:11:"chat_log_id";s:7:"1331690";s:12:"chat_room_id";s:1:"4";s:7:"user_id";s:2:"38";s:6:"handle";s:9:"StarOcean";s:12:"character_id";s:3:"223";s:17:"recipient_user_id";N;s:18:"recipient_username";N;s:4:"text";s:350:"&quot;Weeeeeeeell..&quot; She drawls out again.. &quot;You wanna just go back to my place instead? I mean, we&#039;re not gonna swim so we&#039;d might as well, and i can show you some of my books and junk.&quot; She really didn&#039;t mind, honestly. Swimming could be done anytime, wasn&#039;t every day she had ponies wanting to hang out with her!";s:9:"timestamp";s:10:"1429931944";s:15:"chat_name_color";s:7:"#ffa100";s:9:"chat_rand";s:11:"14299319409";s:15:"chat_text_color";s:7:"#ff7400";s:16:"chat_log_type_id";s:1:"1";s:6:"viewed";N;}i:1331692;a:14:{s:11:"chat_log_id";s:7:"1331692";s:12:"chat_room_id";s:1:"4";s:7:"user_id";s:5:"12019";s:6:"handle";s:4:"Ezki";s:12:"character_id";s:4:"1337";s:17:"recipient_user_id";N;s:18:"recipient_username";N;s:4:"text";s:207:"/me smiles and says &quot;I vould like that very much Miss Ocean!&quot; with a nod. She blinks and says &quot;I do not really need to see your junk though.. unless this means something I am unavare of.&quot;";s:9:"timestamp";s:10:"1429932010";s:15:"chat_name_color";s:7:"#9999ff";s:9:"chat_rand";s:11:"14299320001";s:15:"chat_text_color";s:7:"#ffffff";s:16:"chat_log_type_id";s:1:"1";s:6:"viewed";N;}i:1331693;a:14:{s:11:"chat_log_id";s:7:"1331693";s:12:"chat_room_id";s:1:"4";s:7:"user_id";s:2:"38";s:6:"handle";s:9:"StarOcean";s:12:"character_id";s:3:"223";s:17:"recipient_user_id";N;s:18:"recipient_username";N;s:4:"text";s:392:"/me squeaks and blushes at that! &quot;U-Ummm, n-no it&#039;s an expression..!&quot; She flails her forelegs a little, opting to move on quickly from that one. &quot;Anywho come on, it&#039;s back a ways, other part of town.&quot; She waves her new maybe-friend on as she turns to head on. &quot;Oh, and just call me Star, yeah? I don&#039;t like sounding old..&quot; She shudders. Old. Ewww.";s:9:"timestamp";s:10:"1429932128";s:15:"chat_name_color";s:7:"#ffa100";s:9:"chat_rand";s:11:"14299321246";s:15:"chat_text_color";s:7:"#ff7400";s:16:"chat_log_type_id";s:1:"1";s:6:"viewed";N;}i:1331694;a:14:{s:11:"chat_log_id";s:7:"1331694";s:12:"chat_room_id";s:1:"4";s:7:"user_id";s:5:"12019";s:6:"handle";s:4:"Ezki";s:12:"character_id";s:4:"1337";s:17:"recipient_user_id";N;s:18:"recipient_username";N;s:4:"text";s:178:"&quot;Oh, I see.&quot; she says blinking and seeming more confused but she follows along. She then gasps and bows her head &quot;My apologies! I did not mean to insult you!&quot;";s:9:"timestamp";s:10:"1429932445";s:15:"chat_name_color";s:7:"#9999ff";s:9:"chat_rand";s:11:"14299324350";s:15:"chat_text_color";s:7:"#ffffff";s:16:"chat_log_type_id";s:1:"1";s:6:"viewed";N;}i:1331696;a:14:{s:11:"chat_log_id";s:7:"1331696";s:12:"chat_room_id";s:1:"4";s:7:"user_id";s:2:"38";s:6:"handle";s:9:"StarOcean";s:12:"character_id";s:3:"223";s:17:"recipient_user_id";N;s:18:"recipient_username";N;s:4:"text";s:239:"/me winces a little bit, feeling awkward. &quot;N-Nono, it&#039;s nothing like that..! I mean, it&#039;s just.. Like.. Idunno, personal preference? Or something. You&#039;re fine, really!&quot; She giggles weakly as they head through town.";s:9:"timestamp";s:10:"1429932691";s:15:"chat_name_color";s:7:"#ffa100";s:9:"chat_rand";s:11:"14299326878";s:15:"chat_text_color";s:7:"#ff7400";s:16:"chat_log_type_id";s:1:"1";s:6:"viewed";N;}i:1331697;a:14:{s:11:"chat_log_id";s:7:"1331697";s:12:"chat_room_id";s:1:"4";s:7:"user_id";s:2:"38";s:6:"handle";s:9:"StarOcean";s:12:"character_id";s:3:"223";s:17:"recipient_user_id";N;s:18:"recipient_username";N;s:4:"text";s:41:"((  room change to industrial, please! ))";s:9:"timestamp";s:10:"1429932711";s:15:"chat_name_color";s:7:"#ffa100";s:9:"chat_rand";s:11:"14299327076";s:15:"chat_text_color";s:7:"#ff7400";s:16:"chat_log_type_id";s:1:"1";s:6:"viewed";N;}}